activities:
Axway collects data from European Union residents through several different departments. Each department collects slightly different information and uses it slightly differently.

•	Human Resources: from individuals seeking employment, or who are in the USA system for employment, such systems receive personal information such as name, email, address, benefits and salary;
•	Marketing: in our internal tools such as marketing email box, which receives personal information such as name, email, address;
•	Cloud: in our trouble ticket system, which receives personal information such as name, email, address;
•	IS/ IT: in several internal tools, such as our one-line self-service purchasing portal, internal travel portal tool, and customer management tool, Wiki database, which receive personal information such as name, email, address.
